Package: modprobe
Title: Moderation Probing Tools
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Noah Greifer [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Noah Greifer <noah@unc.edu>
Description: Tools for probing interactions in linear regression analysis. 
    Replicates the functions for moderation at http://quantpsy.org/medn.htm. 
    These include calculation, testing, and plotting of simple slopes, and 
    the Johnson-Neyman technique for computing significance bounds.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1)
Imports:
    ggplot2 (>= 2.2.0),
    gtools
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
License: GPL (>=2)
URL: http://github.com/ngreifer/modprobe
BugReports: http://github.com/ngreifer/modprobe/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Date: XXXX-XX-XX
VignetteBuilder: knitr
